  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_301",
    "english": "Demon. Chieftess of a high-ranking Oni clan known as the \"Frost Phantoms\". The name \"Ragnarok\" is passed down from the legend-ary king who unified the Frost Phantoms in the past. Her real name is \"Shinmora\". She fell in love with a Taimanin from the human world and gave birth to Freya, whom she still watches over.\n\nShe's the strongest swordsman among the Frost Phantoms, using the demonic frost blade \"Laevatein\". She displays formidable power, Combining the Frost Phantom's unique frost magic and swordsmanship.  Additionally, she founded a demon mafia called \"Banshee\" onsisting of Frost Phantoms, where she serves as their boss.",
    "japanese": "Demon. Chieftess of a high-ranking Oni clan known as the \"Frost Phantoms\". The name \"Ragnarok\" is passed down from the legend-ary king who unified the Frost Phantoms in the past. Her real name is \"Shinmora\". She fell in love with a Taimanin from the human world and gave birth to Freya, whom she still watches over.\n\nShe's the strongest swordsman among the Frost Phantoms, using the demonic frost blade \"Laevatein\". She displays formidable power, Combining the Frost Phantom's unique frost magic and swordsmanship.  Additionally, she founded a demon mafia called \"Banshee\" onsisting of Frost Phantoms, where she serves as their boss.",
    "korean": "Demon. Chieftess of a high-ranking Oni clan known as the \"Frost Phantoms\". The name \"Ragnarok\" is passed down from the legend-ary king who unified the Frost Phantoms in the past. Her real name is \"Shinmora\". She fell in love with a Taimanin from the human world and gave birth to Freya, whom she still watches over.\n\nShe's the strongest swordsman among the Frost Phantoms, using the demonic frost blade \"Laevatein\". She displays formidable power, Combining the Frost Phantom's unique frost magic and swordsmanship.  Additionally, she founded a demon mafia called \"Banshee\" onsisting of Frost Phantoms, where she serves as their boss.",
    "chinese_simplified": "Demon. Chieftess of a high-ranking Oni clan known as the \"Frost Phantoms\". The name \"Ragnarok\" is passed down from the legend-ary king who unified the Frost Phantoms in the past. Her real name is \"Shinmora\". She fell in love with a Taimanin from the human world and gave birth to Freya, whom she still watches over.\n\nShe's the strongest swordsman among the Frost Phantoms, using the demonic frost blade \"Laevatein\". She displays formidable power, Combining the Frost Phantom's unique frost magic and swordsmanship.  Additionally, she founded a demon mafia called \"Banshee\" onsisting of Frost Phantoms, where she serves as their boss.",
    "chinese_traditional": "Demon. Chieftess of a high-ranking Oni clan known as the \"Frost Phantoms\". The name \"Ragnarok\" is passed down from the legend-ary king who unified the Frost Phantoms in the past. Her real name is \"Shinmora\". She fell in love with a Taimanin from the human world and gave birth to Freya, whom she still watches over.\n\nShe's the strongest swordsman among the Frost Phantoms, using the demonic frost blade \"Laevatein\". She displays formidable power, Combining the Frost Phantom's unique frost magic and swordsmanship.  Additionally, she founded a demon mafia called \"Banshee\" onsisting of Frost Phantoms, where she serves as their boss.",
    "spanish": "Demon. Chieftess of a high-ranking Oni clan known as the \"Frost Phantoms\". The name \"Ragnarok\" is passed down from the legend-ary king who unified the Frost Phantoms in the past. Her real name is \"Shinmora\". She fell in love with a Taimanin from the human world and gave birth to Freya, whom she still watches over.\n\nShe's the strongest swordsman among the Frost Phantoms, using the demonic frost blade \"Laevatein\". She displays formidable power, Combining the Frost Phantom's unique frost magic and swordsmanship.  Additionally, she founded a demon mafia called \"Banshee\" onsisting of Frost Phantoms, where she serves as their boss."
